WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: 7go_PbI99ok

NOTE Language: en

1
00:00:01.937 --> 00:00:07.325
Sahaj Marriages 1995-1228,
Ganapatipule (India)

2
00:54:02.971 --> 00:54:11.412
It's very great to see that the number
of marriages are increasing,

3
00:54:11.613 --> 00:54:19.536
and you people have very happily accepted
the choice you have made.

4
00:54:19.753 --> 00:54:21.451
It's not final.

5
00:54:21.451 --> 00:54:32.195
Even now you have full freedom to say no
to your weddings.

6
00:54:33.312 --> 00:54:36.312
It's still time.

7
00:54:39.665 --> 00:54:43.682
There are some things we must understand
for Sahaj marriages.

8
00:54:44.570 --> 00:54:48.269
It's not like other marriages, it's very
different,

9
00:54:48.269 --> 00:54:55.891
and for the Sahaj marriages we have to
know how to deal with it also,

10
00:54:56.726 --> 00:55:08.407
because these marriages are done for us to
have children of very high spiritual level


11
00:55:08.407 --> 00:55:10.438
to be born to you, one thing.


12
00:55:10.438 --> 00:55:18.619
Secondly, by marriages to settle you
people into proper ships.

13
00:55:19.808 --> 00:55:24.811
Thirdly, we have to have our Sahaj
culture.

14
00:55:28.479 --> 00:55:31.479
In the Sahaj culture.

15
00:55:31.858 --> 00:55:37.126
We have to understand that it is
allowed to have a divorce.

16
00:55:37.126 --> 00:55:43.642
We don't say no in case something goes
absolutely wrong between the two persons,

17
00:55:43.642 --> 00:55:46.642
but that's no criteria.


18
00:55:47.585 --> 00:55:53.524
Normally I've seen that marriages break
firstly

19
00:55:53.524 --> 00:56:01.958
because some men or women are extremely
aggressive and they aggress each other.

20
00:56:05.154 --> 00:56:08.998
This aggression is just as a temperament.


21
00:56:10.356 --> 00:56:15.458
So the men should not think that women
have come here as slaves or anything.

22
00:56:15.980 --> 00:56:18.064
They are your companions,


23
00:56:18.225 --> 00:56:20.164
and as I've told many a times,

24
00:56:20.164 --> 00:56:24.604
that you are like the two wheels of a chariot,


25
00:56:24.604 --> 00:56:27.604
one on the left, another on the right.


26
00:56:27.604 --> 00:56:31.353
The left wheel, if it becomes smaller,


27
00:56:32.092 --> 00:56:35.092
then the chariot will go round and round.


28
00:56:36.105 --> 00:56:38.580
Moreover, they are similar,


29
00:56:38.580 --> 00:56:41.580
but left is left and right is right.


30
00:56:42.090 --> 00:56:47.543
So first thing, you must respect your
marriage, your wife,

31
00:56:47.543 --> 00:56:52.041
not for superficial things but for her
deeper life.

32
00:56:52.041 --> 00:56:55.041
Respect is very important.

33
00:56:55.041 --> 00:56:58.850
That will also fix your attention,

34
00:56:58.850 --> 00:57:01.850
because as you know, some marriages have been
broken

35
00:57:01.850 --> 00:57:06.761
because the boys or the girls didn't have
good attention

36
00:57:06.761 --> 00:57:11.649
and they were looking at other men or
women.

37
00:57:11.649 --> 00:57:16.174
That sort of thing no Sahaja Yogi is going
to tolerate,

38
00:57:16.174 --> 00:57:18.375
nor is it going to work out.

39
00:57:18.375 --> 00:57:22.812
If you have all such bad habits, you
should cancel your marriage just now.

40
00:57:22.812 --> 00:57:25.812
But later on, if I hear like this,

41
00:57:25.812 --> 00:57:29.633
I'll have to tell you that this is not
possible in Sahaja Yoga.

42
00:57:29.633 --> 00:57:35.098
First of all. The basis of marriage is absolute
morality.

43
00:57:35.098 --> 00:57:36.845
Whatever has happened has happened.


44
00:57:36.845 --> 00:57:41.276
You need not discuss your past, don't tell
anything about your past or anything.

45
00:57:41.276 --> 00:57:42.779
Finished is finished,


46
00:57:42.779 --> 00:57:46.645
because it's not easy for people to bear
the past also.

47
00:57:46.645 --> 00:57:49.078
So better not tell them about your past,


48
00:57:49.078 --> 00:57:53.071
but from today you start a new life
afresh,

49
00:57:53.071 --> 00:57:58.286
where you respect your wife and above all
you must love her.

50
00:57:58.286 --> 00:58:02.122
You must love her more than anybody else.


51
00:58:02.482 --> 00:58:08.854
Because what I find is that many men are
like this in Sahaja Yoga also,

52
00:58:08.854 --> 00:58:10.679
who neglect their wives always,


53
00:58:10.679 --> 00:58:13.562
and some marriages have been broken
because of that.

54
00:58:13.562 --> 00:58:19.244
So first of all, you must pay full
attention to her and love her,

55
00:58:20.985 --> 00:58:23.744
and they should also do the same thing.


56
00:58:23.744 --> 00:58:26.744
It's not only one sided.


57
00:58:26.744 --> 00:58:33.119
And this love and respect must be
understood very well.

58
00:58:33.119 --> 00:58:40.084
Sometimes I have seen some of the people
who spoil their wives very much also.

59
00:58:40.084 --> 00:58:44.745
Like some of the women are
coming from very poor families

60
00:58:44.745 --> 00:58:47.803
or something, so they spoil their
husbands,

61
00:58:47.803 --> 00:58:50.294
or the husbands spoil them.

62
00:58:50.294 --> 00:58:54.859
This is how you get deviated from the real
path of Sahaja Yoga.

63
00:58:54.859 --> 00:59:01.050
What you have to do is to be careful not
to spoil.

64
00:59:01.050 --> 00:59:03.730
Love can never spoil a person,

65
00:59:03.730 --> 00:59:08.109
but if any one of you are aggressive,


66
00:59:08.109 --> 00:59:14.744
then this love can go to another limit of
spoiling the wife,

67
00:59:14.744 --> 00:59:21.498
because you think that's the way you can
dominate your wife or your husband.

68
00:59:22.243 --> 00:59:25.322
I know you are quite wise and you got your
realization,

69
00:59:25.322 --> 00:59:29.581
and we have seen you, for two years you
have been behaving very well,

70
00:59:29.581 --> 00:59:38.455
and you should not be in any way that you should miss out the joy of marriage.

71
00:59:38.455 --> 00:59:40.610
Even if you have the whole world with you,


72
00:59:40.610 --> 00:59:45.384
and if you just don't care with whom you
are married,

73
00:59:45.384 --> 00:59:49.963
you just are busy with something else,
marriages can be spoilt.

74
00:59:49.963 --> 00:59:51.161
It has happened.


75
00:59:51.161 --> 00:59:53.899
So you must pay attention to your wife,


76
00:59:53.899 --> 00:59:56.899
treat her as part and parcel of your
being.

77
00:59:56.899 --> 01:00:01.429
And always don't be self-conscious.


78
01:00:01.429 --> 01:00:04.429
Don't be all the time talking about
yourself,

79
01:00:04.429 --> 01:00:09.105
but also listen to her and also do the
things that she wants, that she likes.

80
01:00:09.105 --> 01:00:16.525
It's very sweetly you can express your
love to her, very sweetly.

81
01:00:18.785 --> 01:00:21.184
There's no need to fight or argue.


82
01:00:21.184 --> 01:00:25.039
We have ashrams where people live for you
and nothing for her.

83
01:00:25.039 --> 01:00:28.768
This kind of a selfish life is not going
to help.

84
01:00:28.768 --> 01:00:31.484
So one has to be very careful


85
01:00:31.484 --> 01:00:36.890
as to how far you try to extract the
energy of your wife

86
01:00:36.890 --> 01:00:39.490
and how much you are going to give her.


87
01:00:39.490 --> 01:00:44.273
Actually, as far as possible, try to do
everything yourself

88
01:00:44.273 --> 01:00:46.460
and try to do something for her also,

89
01:00:46.460 --> 01:00:51.123
because she is a wife and she is a weak
person, she is a woman,

90
01:00:51.123 --> 01:00:52.696
and a woman can't do everything.

91
01:00:52.696 --> 01:00:55.696
For example, she can't lift a suitcase,
she can't do this thing.

92
01:00:55.696 --> 01:01:00.354
The more you work, the more you adjust
yourself,

93
01:01:00.354 --> 01:01:02.669
the more she has energy to do other
things

94
01:01:02.669 --> 01:01:04.525
like cooking, looking after children.


95
01:01:04.525 --> 01:01:07.049
These are very important things,


96
01:01:07.049 --> 01:01:10.415
especially looking after children is very,
very important.

97
01:01:10.415 --> 01:01:14.888
So if you are like that, who gets
irritated very soon

98
01:01:14.888 --> 01:01:21.470
and is very self-conscious and wants
everything to be done only for yourself,

99
01:01:21.470 --> 01:01:22.747
should not marry in Sahaja Yoga.

100
01:01:22.747 --> 01:01:24.269
You can marry outside,


101
01:01:24.269 --> 01:01:29.002
because I don't want Sahaja Yoginis to be
tortured by you by any chance.

102
01:01:29.002 --> 01:01:31.111
I've organized this marriage.

103
01:01:31.111 --> 01:01:35.595
Marriages are not only for you but for
them also,

104
01:01:35.595 --> 01:01:38.097
and they expect certain things from you.


105
01:01:38.097 --> 01:01:40.583
They have dreams about a husband.


106
01:01:40.583 --> 01:01:43.329
They think that our husband will do this.


107
01:01:43.329 --> 01:01:47.173
There's no harm in taking them round and
being kind to them,

108
01:01:47.173 --> 01:01:48.642
you'll enjoy that.

109
01:01:48.642 --> 01:01:51.883
Try to see that she's sharing your life


110
01:01:51.883 --> 01:01:54.883
and you should share her life in a proper
way.

111
01:01:56.180 --> 01:01:59.821
Then we have conditionings of our own
country also.

112
01:01:59.821 --> 01:02:07.846
Sometimes, say, we have some people who
are from America,

113
01:02:07.846 --> 01:02:13.964
some are from Italy, some are from
England, Switzerland.

114
01:02:13.964 --> 01:02:19.663
So those conditionings should not be put
on your wives.

115
01:02:19.663 --> 01:02:23.557
Whatever you are, you look after that
part,

116
01:02:23.557 --> 01:02:26.880
but don't in any way hurt your wife,

117
01:02:26.880 --> 01:02:32.887
that she comes from a lower type of
culture, this, that.

118
01:02:32.887 --> 01:02:38.372
For us the culture is within ourselves,
not without, not outside.

119
01:02:38.372 --> 01:02:41.603
And all the problems we have faced so far


120
01:02:41.603 --> 01:02:46.541
is because we do not respect the culture
of other people.

121
01:02:46.541 --> 01:02:52.473
We want our wives to be, just be one part
of that culture.

122
01:02:52.473 --> 01:02:57.942
All this I'm telling you because I want
you all to be happy

123
01:02:57.942 --> 01:03:00.032
and enjoy your wives.

124
01:03:00.032 --> 01:03:05.243
Because even if you give the greatest wealth of enjoyment.

125
01:03:05.243 --> 01:03:09.268
And if you don't enjoy, then who is
responsible for that?

126
01:03:10.139 --> 01:03:13.139
So the marriage in Sahaja Yoga is for
enjoyment.

127
01:03:13.139 --> 01:03:17.277
Enjoyment of companionship, enjoyment of
love,

128
01:03:17.277 --> 01:03:23.464
enjoyment of sharing every part of your
activity.

129
01:03:23.464 --> 01:03:26.464
Nothing is more important than sharing.


130
01:03:26.464 --> 01:03:30.839
This will really help you to lead a very
happy,

131
01:03:30.839 --> 01:03:33.839
joyous and prosperous married life.


132
01:03:33.839 --> 01:03:38.639
I wish you all good luck and all the good
sense, wisdom,

133
01:03:38.639 --> 01:03:42.787
that you will enjoy your married life and
prosper in it.

134
01:03:42.787 --> 01:03:45.787
May God bless you.

135
01:04:20.983 --> 01:04:25.868
So enjoy every moment now, all right?

136
02:00:25.296 --> 02:00:30.589
You are all ready to get married

137
02:00:30.810 --> 02:00:36.404
and I bless you from My heart.

138
02:00:38.050 --> 02:00:43.506
Now, the duty of a wife I need not tell
you, you know it very well.

139
02:00:43.707 --> 02:00:52.112
I've told many a times that she is
responsible to build the society of Sahaj.

140
02:00:52.708 --> 02:00:57.209
And as a result, she has a very great
responsibility.

141
02:00:57.410 --> 02:01:04.743
She has to look after the whole family,
the relations of the husband,

142
02:01:04.944 --> 02:01:16.941
and should go up to the great expectations
of the family members also.

143
02:01:17.142 --> 02:01:20.923
This can be done if you have really love
for people.

144
02:01:21.124 --> 02:01:25.394
If you have love, you wlll have tolerance
and you’ll be able

145
02:01:25.595 --> 02:01:31.050
to bring more people in Sahaja Yoga who
are related to you and to your husband

146
02:01:31.251 --> 02:01:38.982
by showing a very good household that
you have created.

147
02:01:43.577 --> 02:01:48.715
Towards the husband you have to be
very dedicated

148
02:01:48.916 --> 02:01:55.795
and don’t tell him about your past.
Past is finished and start afresh.

149
02:01:55.996 --> 02:02:01.132
It’s a very dangerous thing to say anything
about your past to your husband.

150
02:02:01.333 --> 02:02:11.029
So, you have your expectations, so he too
has his own expectations about you.

151
02:02:11.230 --> 02:02:15.479
Expectations should not be there
in Sahaja Yoga.

152
02:02:15.680 --> 02:02:22.284
But gradually, if you understand the value
of your marriage and you respect it,

153
02:02:22.485 --> 02:02:26.586
then you will not go after superficial
things.

154
02:02:26.787 --> 02:02:36.449
You’ll not ask him to buy this, buy that
for you on a material level.

155
02:02:36.719 --> 02:02:43.361
But also on the mental level you should
not try to judge him,

156
02:02:43.570 --> 02:02:47.175
but as you are spiritual, he is also
spiritual.

157
02:02:47.376 --> 02:02:50.541
So, you should see his vibrations.

158
02:02:50.742 --> 02:02:57.413
Don’t tell him but try to correct it slowly
and steadily.

159
02:02:57.614 --> 02:03:05.461
It’s easy to complain about married life,
very easy, and it’s a very common thing.

160
02:03:05.662 --> 02:03:10.049
If there are two ladies who are
dissatisfied with their married life,

161
02:03:10.250 --> 02:03:18.999
can create a big number of people who
will be complaining about marriages.

162
02:03:19.200 --> 02:03:26.150
So, one has to be very watchful and
careful not to indulge into gossips

163
02:03:26.351 --> 02:03:32.807
and talking about some things which has
no meaning in Sahaja Yoga.

164
02:03:33.008 --> 02:03:37.959
Going to the higher life, we have to see
that, as we are spiritual people

165
02:03:38.160 --> 02:03:41.933
we have to keep our spirituality growing
and growing

166
02:03:42.134 --> 02:03:45.928
so that great souls who want to be born
on this earth

167
02:03:46.129 --> 02:03:49.133
will take birth in your families.

168
02:03:49.334 --> 02:03:52.633
But that doesn’t mean, if you just get
attached to your own child,

169
02:03:52.834 --> 02:03:56.905
then others' children are not to be loved.

170
02:03:57.106 --> 02:04:02.537
Love doesn’t limit you, so you have to love
others' children also.

171
02:04:02.738 --> 02:04:05.890
The guests who come in your house,
you must look after.

172
02:04:06.091 --> 02:04:08.791
It is your duty to look after the guests.

173
02:04:08.992 --> 02:04:15.700
They are Sahaja Yogis, you have no business
to insult them or to trouble them.

174
02:04:15.901 --> 02:04:22.360
Your successful married life is going
to help so many people in this world.

175
02:04:22.561 --> 02:04:27.698
We have to show that Sahaja Yoga marriages
are extremely successful,

176
02:04:27.899 --> 02:04:31.917
peaceful and full of joy.

177
02:04:32.118 --> 02:04:36.407
If you want to find faults, you see,
there is no end to it.

178
02:04:36.608 --> 02:04:41.709
But it’s better to see your own faults
and correct yourself.

179
02:04:41.910 --> 02:04:50.819
Of course, if there is any problem which is
not soluble, which is absolutely difficult,

180
02:04:51.020 --> 02:04:56.369
then you can let Me know and I’ll try
to solve it if possible.

181
02:04:56.570 --> 02:05:02.309
Otherwise, you can depart. But it’s a very
last, extreme case.

182
02:05:02.510 --> 02:05:06.916
It’s the wife who makes the family,
she makes the marriage very good.

183
02:05:07.117 --> 02:05:11.683
So, it is for you to decide. Now, even now,
there is time,

184
02:05:11.884 --> 02:05:14.976
if you don’t want to marry, you don’t like
your husbands

185
02:05:15.177 --> 02:05:19.254
or in any way you think he is not
all right, you can decide now.

186
02:05:19.455 --> 02:05:23.393
There is time still for you to decide.

187
02:05:23.594 --> 02:05:27.843
We have to prove that our marriages,
Indian marriages,

188
02:05:28.044 --> 02:05:33.332
are not Indian: they are universal
marriages,

189
02:05:33.533 --> 02:05:40.689
and they are to be treated with that great
sense of responsibility.

190
02:05:41.913 --> 02:05:48.157
Once you understand your responsibility,
I’m sure you will know what is to be done.

191
02:05:48.358 --> 02:05:54.640
Firstly, you should never argue with your
husband, as far as possible.

192
02:05:54.841 --> 02:06:02.553
You should not shout at him; you should
not be disrespectful for him before others.

193
02:06:02.754 --> 02:06:07.059
And relationship between you and your
husband is a secret;

194
02:06:07.260 --> 02:06:13.204
it should not be discussed
on the cross-roads, you see.

195
02:06:13.405 --> 02:06:18.075
Let people see for themselves how happy
you are.

196
02:06:18.276 --> 02:06:20.820
But there is no need to be artificially
happy.

197
02:06:21.021 --> 02:06:23.492
There is no need to be artificially
suffering.

198
02:06:23.693 --> 02:06:26.769
There is no suffering that is allowed
in Sahaja Yoga,

199
02:06:26.970 --> 02:06:29.729
so if you think something is wrong...
[cut in the video].

200
02:06:29.930 --> 02:06:33.170
… is done, it is sinful. One should never
do like that;

201
02:06:33.370 --> 02:06:38.214
you are married in Sahaja Yoga not
to separate your husband from collectivity.

202
02:06:38.415 --> 02:06:45.443
There’s more enjoyment, more sharing
and no pressure

203
02:06:45.644 --> 02:06:48.797
if you all enjoy the collectivity.

204
02:06:48.998 --> 02:06:55.732
I know you are all very wise and good girls
and you will look after your family life

205
02:06:55.933 --> 02:07:01.071
and your social life and also look after
your husband.

206
02:07:01.272 --> 02:07:08.704
But you should also look after other people
and try to understand your problems:

207
02:07:08.905 --> 02:07:13.392
what problems you have, you had. And then
try to solve them

208
02:07:13.593 --> 02:07:18.169
so that those who come to your house
or those who are in contact with you

209
02:07:18.370 --> 02:07:23.410
will be specially blessed by your Gruha
Lakshmi quality.

210
02:07:23.611 --> 02:07:27.759
In a collective way you must meditate.
You must meditate at home

211
02:07:27.960 --> 02:07:34.755
and you must go to every meditation centre
whenever it is necessary.

212
02:07:34.956 --> 02:07:38.750
I’ve seen the women in Sahaja Yoga are
rather poor for spirituality,

213
02:07:38.950 --> 02:07:43.727
it’s very surprising. I am Myself a woman
and I can’t understand

214
02:07:43.928 --> 02:07:48.834
that they are so busy, you see, doing
all other things but not meditation.

215
02:07:49.035 --> 02:07:53.490
So, you have to become gems in Sahaja Yoga.
In spirituality you have to rise.

216
02:07:53.691 --> 02:07:56.001
For that you must meditate at home

217
02:07:56.202 --> 02:08:03.108
and also go to all the collective
programmes you have.

218
02:08:03.309 --> 02:08:06.967
This will help you a lot, help you,
your children;

219
02:08:07.168 --> 02:08:09.117
they will become very good children,

220
02:08:09.318 --> 02:08:17.069
and their whole standard of life will be
very much higher and spiritual.

221
02:08:17.270 --> 02:08:21.941
We have to create these great families.
That’s why I was insisting

222
02:08:22.142 --> 02:08:25.773
that we should have marriages here.
But by this, if we have

223
02:08:25.974 --> 02:08:30.481
all the other kind of useless marriages,
it’s better not to have.

224
02:08:30.682 --> 02:08:34.478
So, I request you to take up
the responsibility of a wife

225
02:08:34.679 --> 02:08:40.436
and look after the whole family, look after
the whole family of Sahaja Yogis.

226
02:08:40.637 --> 02:08:46.220
And apart from that, you have to think
what you can contribute to Sahaja Yoga.

227
02:08:46.421 --> 02:08:49.887
We have some very great women who have
done a lot,

228
02:08:50.088 --> 02:08:52.750
who are married women, done a lot
for Sahaja Yoga.

229
02:08:52.950 --> 02:08:59.718
In the same way, you should take up upon
yourself to do Sahaja Yoga work

230
02:08:59.919 --> 02:09:03.357
and Sahaja Yoga expansion.

231
02:09:03.558 --> 02:09:08.791
I hope you understand how important
you are in Sahaja Yoga.

232
02:09:08.992 --> 02:09:15.139
After all, this husband is more busy
outside

233
02:09:15.340 --> 02:09:20.596
and maybe he might little bit neglect you.
But that doesn’t mean that he neglects;

234
02:09:20.797 --> 02:09:24.474
you must understand that he has to work
hard and this and that.

235
02:09:24.675 --> 02:09:28.550
Also, there's the demand on his time,
demand on his money

236
02:09:28.750 --> 02:09:32.435
should be minimum, minimum that is
possible.

237
02:09:32.636 --> 02:09:37.178
But if the husband is absolutely careless
about you, and doesn’t bother about you

238
02:09:37.379 --> 02:09:40.082
or he dominates you or troubles you,
tortures you;

239
02:09:40.283 --> 02:09:45.353
in any way if you are unhappy, you are
open, absolutely open to write to Me

240
02:09:45.554 --> 02:09:47.275
about all that is happening,

241
02:09:47.476 --> 02:09:53.610
because I’ll try to correct him and I’ll
try to see what is the problem inside.

242
02:09:54.485 --> 02:09:59.114
The last thing one has to know is that
a woman has to be extremely moral.

243
02:09:59.323 --> 02:10:03.753
She has to be extremely moral. If she
becomes immoral,

244
02:10:03.954 --> 02:10:07.448
the husband will become immoral,
the children will become immoral.

245
02:10:07.649 --> 02:10:12.394
So, you have to stick onto your morality,
be proud of it and you can do it

246
02:10:12.595 --> 02:10:16.058
because God has given you a special
quality.

247
02:10:16.259 --> 02:10:20.891
So, it is your duty to keep great morality
in the family

248
02:10:21.092 --> 02:10:32.077
and to live like good citizens of your
country, citizens of Sahaja Yoga family.

249
02:10:32.278 --> 02:10:38.235
I bless you all with My heart again
and please accept what I’ve said.

250
02:10:38.436 --> 02:10:43.493
If you don’t want, even now, not to marry,
you can decide that;

251
02:10:43.694 --> 02:10:48.379
if possible, I will try to remove this out.

252
02:10:48.580 --> 02:10:51.333
Thank you very much. May God bless you.
